                                    "id": "id-overview-text",
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Kernel is a React 19 landing page built to demonstrate production-level frontend architecture. The project focuses on three engineering concerns: scroll-driven animation orchestration, a modular component system, and a consistent design language applied across all UI states. Every component is custom — no UI library was used."
