                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "A terminal-style preloader that simulates system initialization. Built as a GSAP timeline with staggered text reveals and a progress bar tied to asset loading state — dismissed on completion, not on a fixed timer."
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "id": "id-feat-scroll",
                            "columnTitle": "Scroll & Interaction",
                            "blocks": [
                                {
                                    "id": "id-scroll-text",
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "Lenis normalizes scroll velocity across devices. ScrollTrigger pins sections and drives parallax transforms. Custom cursor tracks mouse position via requestAnimationFrame with lerp smoothing — no CSS transitions involved."
                                }
                            ]
                        }
